<ul class="marLeft1">
<li  class="paraStyle1">Admission will be granted till the availability of seats on a first come first serve basis.</li>
<li  class="paraStyle1">There will be a student and parent interaction for those who have registered their wards.</li>
<li  class="paraStyle1">Students applying under section134(A) should contact the Directorate of School Education, Haryana.</li>
</ul>

<p class="paraStyle3"><b>For admission to Pre-Nursery and Nursery</b></p>
<ul class="marLeft1">
<li  class="paraStyle1">There will be parent interactions along with the child with the Administrator / Principal of the School.</li>
</ul>

<p class="paraStyle3"><b>For admission to KG and above</b></p>
<ul class="marLeft1">
<li  class="paraStyle1">There will be an age-appropriate assessment (written as well as oral assessment) through evaluative worksheets that will test the general comprehension levels of the child.</li>
</ul>
<p class="paraStyle1"><b>NOTE: Interaction with the school Administrator or Principal will not guarantee admission.</b></p>
